VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT android:scheme\s*=\s*"(?!https?)[^"]+"|<data\s[^>]*android:host\s*=
WHEN EXPR MISSING:android:autoVerify\s*=\s*"true" && MISSING:android:exported\s*=\s*"false"
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects custom URI scheme deep links without Android App Links autoVerify, which allows any app to intercept them.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Deep Link Without App Link Verification.
